{{Infobox Korean settlement | title = Ahyeon-dong | img = Ahyeon-dong Comunity Service Center 20140514 151959.JPG | imgwidth = | imgcaption = Ahyeon-dong Community Service Center (Mapo-gu) | hangul = {{linktext|아|현|동}} | hanja = {{linktext|阿|峴|洞}} | rr = Ahyeon-dong | mr = Ahyeon-tong | area_km2 = 0.79 | pop = 36519 | popnote = <ref name="encyber" /> | popyear = 2001 | popden_km2 = | popdennote = | divs = | map = |mapcaption = }}
'''Ahyeon-dong''' is a ''[[dong (neighbourhood)|dong]]'', neighbourhood of [[Mapo-gu]] in [[Seoul]], [[South Korea]].<ref name="encyber">{{cite web|url=http://www.encyber.com/search_w/ctdetail.php?masterno=732165&contentno=732165 |title=아현동 (Ahyeon-dong 阿峴洞) |publisher=Doosan Encyclopedia |accessdate=2008-04-22 |language=Korean }}{{dead link|date=June 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref name="Mapo-gu">{{cite web|url=http://www.mapo.go.kr/Design/html/e_ward/04_mapo_origin02_01.jsp |publisher=Mapo-gu official site |title= The origin of the dong' name (Ahyeon-dong 아현동)|accessdate=2008-04-22 |language=Korean|}}</ref>
